---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Private Poker Night - Rules & Etiquette" description="Learn the rules and etiquette for our private poker night event">
<div class="bg-base-100 rounded-box p-6 shadow-lg mb-8">
    <div class="bg-amber-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-amber-200">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-amber-800">Event Rules & Consensual Game Etiquette</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-amber-700">This is the most important section. To ensure a fun and comfortable experience for everyone, please review the following essential rules on safety and consent. Adherence is non-negotiable.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-amber-900 p-4 bg-amber-100 rounded-md">Consent is mandatory for everything.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>No Unwanted Contact:</strong> Includes all forms of physical touch, suggestive body gestures, and inappropriate or unwanted speech.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Host's Authority:</strong> The host ("The Princess") rules the Palace. If the host feels uncomfortable for any reason, you will be asked to leave.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Ongoing Consent:</strong> A visible item will signify ongoing consent. If anyone feels uncomfortable, the game will pause until consent from all players is re-established.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Behavior Policy:</strong> You will receive **one warning** for out-of-line behavior. A second instance means you will be asked to leave.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Collective Safety:</strong> If someone is asked to leave, you are expected to side with the host. We collectively create a safe space.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Nudity Is Not an Invitation:</strong> Nudity is a consequence of the game, not an invitation for contact. Players may redress at the end of a round.</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>